chapter.section:
       Workspace Queries



Most workspace query procedures output a "contents list", which can be used as input to the Workspace Inspection procedures.
All procedures whose input is indicated as "contentslist" will accept any of the following:


A single word (taken as a procedure name)
A list of words (taken as procedure names)
A list of two lists (taken as procedure names and variable names, respectivly)
A list of three lists (taken as procedure names, variable names, and property list names, respectivly)




       &command-contents;
       &command-buried;
       &command-procedures;
       &command-names;
       &command-plists;
       &command-namelist;
       &command-pllist;
